The Daily Kick app brings you all the best soccer stories and breaking news from the heavyweights of digital publishing including Daily Sun, Soccer Laduma, Kickoff, News24 and Sports24 as well as thousands of other local and international sites. The aggregator app is smart, light on data and super-fast. Users choose their interests and receive personalised content. The more they use the app, the better the app gets at serving content that is relevant to the individual user. The app's high level of personalisation even allows sports fans to choose teams or publications to follow for score predictions, fixtures, news and celebrity gossip. There are article summaries and content can be downloaded for viewing offline. Daily Kick is a product of 24.com and is available for free download on Apple and Android devices. For more info or to download the app click here.